<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.259135>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Aphelochaeta antelonga sp. nov. A, holotype (MCZ 132794); Aphelochaeta guimondi sp. nov. B-C, holotype (MCZ 132798). A, anterior end, dorsal view; B, anterior end, dorsal view; C, anterior end, lateral view. Scale bars: A ‒ C = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/259135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.259136>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Aphelochaeta antelonga sp. nov. A – B, paratype (MCZ 132795); Aphelochaeta glandaria C, voucher specimen (MCZ 132797); Aphelochaeta guimondi sp. nov. D, paratype (MCZ 132799). A, anterior end, lateral view; B, neurosetae, setiger 4. C, neurosetae, setiger 2. D, noto- and neurosetae, mid body. Scale bars: A = 200 µm, B = 5 µm, C = 10 µm, D = 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/259136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.259137>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Aphelochaeta antelonga sp. nov. A, Paratype MZUCR 132794; Aphelochaeta glandaria B, voucher specimen (MCZ 132797); Aphelochaeta guimondi sp. nov. C, Holotype MCZ 132798; Aphelochaeta praeacuta sp. nov. D, Holotype MCZ 132801; Aphelochaeta striata sp. nov. E, Holotype MCZ 132803; Aphelochaeta zebra sp. nov. F, Holotype MCZ 132807. A, MGSP of anterior end, ventral view; B, MGSP of anterior end, dorsal view; C, MGSP of anterior end, ventral view; D, MGSP of anterior end, ventral view; E, MGSP of anterior end, ventral view; F, MGSP of anterior end, ventral view. Scale bars; A ‒ F = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/259137/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

